Class PropertyBasedSpnegoLoginService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.jetty.util.component.AbstractLifeCycle
      • org.eclipse.jetty.security.SpnegoLoginService
        • org.apache.calcite.avatica.server.PropertyBasedSpnegoLoginService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.eclipse.jetty.security.LoginService, org.eclipse.jetty.util.component.LifeCycle

    public class PropertyBasedSpnegoLoginService
extends org.eclipse.jetty.security.SpnegoLoginService
    A customization of SpnegoLoginService which directly specifies the server's principal instead of requiring a file to exist. Known to work with Jetty-9.2.x, any other version would require testing/inspection to ensure the logic is still sound.
